name: Agent
line: Morty, I'm seeing more croc than human here.

name: Rick
line: That's enough! We don't want you injuring your ball-throwing arm!

name: Rick
line: Rick, you have a new mission.

name: Rick
line: Yeah, I know. I know how to vacuum. I vacuum Mom and Dad. I've been doing it for six months!

name: Rick
line: You were right! We were wrong! We both were right!!

name: Agent
line: Oh man, oh, man, I can't believe we're sitting around, standing around in Mr. Goldenfold's house. It's really weird.

name: Rick
line: Hey, Morty! Look at this guy go. He's smart. He knows we can do everything.

name: Agent
line: He knows we could do better! We could put him on a watch list or something.
